*[auto_tests/onion_test.c, line 482 at r1](https://reviewable.io:443/reviews/toktok/c-toxcore/689#-L2rWfTUv9Trz5TLS5HK:-L2rWfTVidis1ByQHJrf:b37fi1s) ([raw file](https://github.com/toktok/c-toxcore/blob/c5e68428bf78d71a4f42fd725f019362245cd5ca/auto_tests/onion_test.c#L482)):*
> ```C
>     printf("adding friend\n");
>     int frnum_f = onion_addfriend(onions[NUM_FIRST]->onion_c,
>                                   nc_get_self_secret_key(onion_get_net_crypto(onions[NUM_LAST]->onion_c)));
> ```

You are passing`self_secret_key` when you should be passing `self_public_key`

*[toxcore/onion_client.c, line 591 at r1](https://reviewable.io:443/reviews/toktok/c-toxcore/689#-L2rY-7OWqsKkAEB7ybG:-L2rY-7Pqv91r5dZFV5x:b-hv7s3z) ([raw file](https://github.com/toktok/c-toxcore/blob/c5e68428bf78d71a4f42fd725f019362245cd5ca/toxcore/onion_client.c#L591)):*

*[toxcore/onion_client.c, line 851 at r1](https://reviewable.io:443/reviews/toktok/c-toxcore/689#-L2rYH4L8gJIJcbmaQoN:-L2rYH4L8gJIJcbmaQoO:bxxx5r2) ([raw file](https://github.com/toktok/c-toxcore/blob/c5e68428bf78d71a4f42fd725f019362245cd5ca/toxcore/onion_client.c#L851)):*
